---
title: Creamy Chicken and Tomato Pasta with Spinach and Cheese
description: This Creamy Chicken and Tomato Pasta is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-and-tomato-pasta-f0b25df6.jpg
